[
  {
    "startTime": 0.0,
    "endTime": 3.0,
    "text": "I don't see how this day could get any weirder and here we go!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 3.0,
    "endTime": 6.0,
    "text": "La, la, la, la, la, la, la, la, la, la..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 6.0,
    "endTime": 7.0,
    "text": "Ah!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 7.0,
    "endTime": 8.0,
    "text": "What's up, dude?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 8.0,
    "endTime": 10.0,
    "text": "Business all messed up!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 10.0,
    "endTime": 10.0,
    "text": "I know, right?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 10.0,
    "endTime": 13.0,
    "text": "I mean, future me, wearing sandals?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 13.0,
    "endTime": 15.0,
    "text": "I mean, you're gonna steal Carrie from me!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 15.0,
    "endTime": 18.0,
    "text": "It's supposed to be Car-win, not Car-bull, you homewrecking woman-eater!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 18.0,
    "endTime": 21.0,
    "text": "And it looks like I didn't stop at women."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 21.0,
    "endTime": 21.0,
    "text": "Ah!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 21.0,
    "endTime": 22.0,
    "text": "I agree."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 26.0,
    "endTime": 29.0,
    "text": "Always thought I was the one wearing the pants in this relationship."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 29.0,
    "endTime": 30.0,
    "text": "What is going on?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 30.0,
    "endTime": 34.0,
    "text": "This mess has got Sarah's name written all over it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 34.0,
    "endTime": 35.0,
    "text": "How do you know?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 35.0,
    "endTime": 35.0,
    "text": "Mm-mm!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 35.0,
    "endTime": 42.0,
    "text": "Her heart pounding in her chest, Penny said to Banana Joe, let's never split!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 42.0,
    "endTime": 46.0,
    "text": "What did you do this time?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 46.0,
    "endTime": 47.0,
    "text": "Nothing, I swear!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 47.0,
    "endTime": 55.0,
    "text": "I was just riding some non-canon AT and AR ships the odd one shot here and there and a bit of OOC, some OC drawings, of course, but mostly OTP squeeze and fan service!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 55.0,
    "endTime": 56.0,
    "text": "Wait, what?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 56.0,
    "endTime": 60.0,
    "text": "I was just writing love stories about everyone in Elmore."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 60.0,
    "endTime": 62.0,
    "text": "I got a bit carried away."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 62.0,
    "endTime": 63.0,
    "text": "Where did you get this?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 63.0,
    "endTime": 66.0,
    "text": "It fell off the back of a truck!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 66.0,
    "endTime": 68.0,
    "text": "That's not a euphemism, it literally did."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 68.0,
    "endTime": 69.0,
    "text": "The awesome story!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 69.0,
    "endTime": 73.0,
    "text": "Well, just take a look at what happened when you rode in it!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 73.0,
    "endTime": 74.0,
    "text": "Wait, wait, wait!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 74.0,
    "endTime": 74.0,
    "text": "I'm an otaku."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 74.0,
    "endTime": 75.0,
    "text": "The light could kill me."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 76.0,
    "endTime": 83.0,
    "text": "It's like a commercial for male deodorant out there!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 83.0,
    "endTime": 84.0,
    "text": "Oh, my gosh!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 84.0,
    "endTime": 87.0,
    "text": "So when I rode all this, it became canon in reality!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 88.0,
    "endTime": 89.0,
    "text": "Excuse me for a second."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 90.0,
    "endTime": 94.0,
    "text": "Well, you've got to fix it, okay?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 94.0,
    "endTime": 94.0,
    "text": "Right!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 94.0,
    "endTime": 100.0,
    "text": "Oh, I probably need to destroy it thoroughly."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 100.0,
    "endTime": 101.0,
    "text": "Are you okay?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 101.0,
    "endTime": 101.0,
    "text": "I'm fine."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 103.0,
    "endTime": 106.0,
    "text": "Ah!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 106.0,
    "endTime": 106.0,
    "text": "Uh, hey!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 106.0,
    "endTime": 113.0,
    "text": "I'm alive and in quite a lot of pain!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 113.0,
    "endTime": 116.0,
    "text": "Okay, so the only solution is to rewrite it back to normal."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 116.0,
    "endTime": 117.0,
    "text": "Open up!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 117.0,
    "endTime": 119.0,
    "text": "This is the police!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 119.0,
    "endTime": 120.0,
    "text": "They're here for the notebook!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 120.0,
    "endTime": 121.0,
    "text": "Then hurry up and start already!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 121.0,
    "endTime": 121.0,
    "text": "Okay!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 121.0,
    "endTime": 122.0,
    "text": "Open up!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 122.0,
    "endTime": 123.0,
    "text": "I've got nothing!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 124.0,
    "endTime": 125.0,
    "text": "What?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 125.0,
    "endTime": 126.0,
    "text": "I've got Ryder's book!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 126.0,
    "endTime": 128.0,
    "text": "You're going to have to do it!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 128.0,
    "endTime": 129.0,
    "text": "Police!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 129.0,
    "endTime": 129.0,
    "text": "Open up!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 129.0,
    "endTime": 134.0,
    "text": "Mr. Small looked at Larry and said, It's not you, Larry."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 134.0,
    "endTime": 134.0,
    "text": "It's me."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 134.0,
    "endTime": 135.0,
    "text": "No, wait, no."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 135.0,
    "endTime": 139.0,
    "text": "Larry said, We can't see each other anymore."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 139.0,
    "endTime": 145.0,
    "text": "It was a hard blow for Mr. Small, and Larry was destroyed."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 145.0,
    "endTime": 146.0,
    "text": "You're making things worse!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 146.0,
    "endTime": 149.0,
    "text": "This is hard!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 149.0,
    "endTime": 154.0,
    "text": "Just keep it simple, like Principal Brown and Jackie Wilson broke up."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 154.0,
    "endTime": 154.0,
    "text": "Scratch that."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 154.0,
    "endTime": 157.0,
    "text": "Take it back together."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 157.0,
    "endTime": 157.0,
    "text": "Ah!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 157.0,
    "endTime": 159.0,
    "text": "They're breaking down the door!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 160.0,
    "endTime": 163.0,
    "text": "I got this!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 163.0,
    "endTime": 164.0,
    "text": "Come on, troopers!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 164.0,
    "endTime": 166.0,
    "text": "Go, go, go!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 166.0,
    "endTime": 168.0,
    "text": "Bring on the light!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 168.0,
    "endTime": 172.0,
    "text": "Good job, dude!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 172.0,
    "endTime": 181.0,
    "text": "I haven't written anything yet, but I'll send a little something to delay them."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 181.0,
    "endTime": 181.0,
    "text": "Come on!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 181.0,
    "endTime": 183.0,
    "text": "Come on, come on, come on!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 183.0,
    "endTime": 183.0,
    "text": "Ah!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 183.0,
    "endTime": 187.0,
    "text": "Bobbert, Jamie and Tina were having a picnic."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 187.0,
    "endTime": 189.0,
    "text": "They knew it would be their last meal together."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 189.0,
    "endTime": 190.0,
    "text": "Don't be so sad."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 190.0,
    "endTime": 191.0,
    "text": "What we had was beautiful."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 191.0,
    "endTime": 192.0,
    "text": "Let's eat, Bobbert, Tina said."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 193.0,
    "endTime": 195.0,
    "text": "Wait, shouldn't there be a comma before Bobbert?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 195.0,
    "endTime": 197.0,
    "text": "What difference does that make?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 197.0,
    "endTime": 203.0,
    "text": "And he said to Joe, It's over, and his stomach twisted into a knot as he cried."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 203.0,
    "endTime": 206.0,
    "text": "Hot Dog Guy and Claire looked at each other with tears in their eyes."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 206.0,
    "endTime": 207.0,
    "text": "We need space, said Claire."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 207.0,
    "endTime": 208.0,
    "text": "I agree, he replied."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 208.0,
    "endTime": 213.0,
    "text": "I'm sorry, but this is moving too fast for me."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 213.0,
    "endTime": 218.0,
    "text": "I'm sorry, but this is moving too fast for me."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 218.0,
    "endTime": 220.0,
    "text": "This bird is out of control!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 220.0,
    "endTime": 221.0,
    "text": "What do you know?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 221.0,
    "endTime": 225.0,
    "text": "And then Yuki said, I'm sorry, but this is moving too fast for me."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 225.0,
    "endTime": 225.0,
    "text": "What?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 225.0,
    "endTime": 234.0,
    "text": "You think you can just lock three people in a room and pressure them to keep coming up with gold?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 234.0,
    "endTime": 234.0,
    "text": " Eventually, they'll start repeating material."
  }
]